<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{لِتَعَارَفُوا}</span> <span class="c4">[١٣]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«أتقاكم»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>{خَبِيرٌ <span class="c2">(١٣)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٣]</span> تام.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{آَمَنَّا}</span> <span class="c4">[١٤]</span> حسن.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{أَسْلَمْنَا}</span> <span class="c4">[١٤]</span> أحسن مما قبله.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{فِي قُلُوبِكُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٤]</span> كاف عند أبي حاتم للابتداء بالشرط،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«شيئًا»</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>{رَحِيمٌ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٤]</span> تام.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c3">{ثُمَّ لَمْ يَرْتَابُوا}</span> <span class="c4">[١٥]</span> حسن.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c3">{فِي سَبِيلِ اللَّهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٥]</span> جائز.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>{الصَّادِقُونَ <span class="c2">(١٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٥]</span> تام؛ إن جعل <span class="c2">«الذين»</span> خبر <span class="c2">«المؤمنون»</span>؛ فإن جعل نعتًا لم يوقف على شيء إلى <span class="c2">«الصادقون»</span>؛ لأن <span class="c2">«أولئك»</span> يكون خبر <span class="c2">«المؤمنون»</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c3">{بِدِينِكُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٦]</span> حسن.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c3">{وَمَا فِي الْأَرْضِ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٦]</span> كاف.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>{عَلِيمٌ <span class="c2">(١٦)</span>} <span class="c4">[١٦]</span> تام؛ على استئناف ما بعده، وجائز إن جعل متصلًا بما قبله.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c3">{أَنْ أَسْلَمُوا}</span> <span class="c4">[١٧]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«إسلامكم»</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c3">{لِلْإِيمَانِ}</span> <span class="c4">[١٧]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأنَّ الشرط الذي بعده جوابه ما قبله.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
